cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.AI, cs.CY 

This paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning techniques applied to financial data. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), which deals with the intersection of computer science and linguistics. The paper also extensively uses deep learning techniques, which makes cs.LG (Machine Learning) a likely category as well. The paper deals with information retrieval and analysis of financial data, which makes cs.IR (Information Retrieval) another possible category. The paper also deals with automated decision-making, which is a common theme in cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper deals with the application of these techniques to finance, which makes cs.CY (Computers and Society) a possible category as well.
